pageContext.claim: “Four witnesses have testified under penalty of perjury that after officials in Detroit announced the last votes had been counted, tens of thousands of additional ballots arrived without required envelopes. Every single one was for a Democrat. I got no votes.”
pageContext.analysis: "Trump's claim presents no evidence of wrongdoing," {noted the Detroit Free Press}. "On Nov. 4, blank ballots were delivered to TCF, according to a response from the legal team representing the city of Detroit in a lawsuit alleging fraud. The blank ballots were used to process ballots cast by members of the military and voters living overseas that have to be copied onto the correct ballot form in order to be counted."
